schools.name: Dr. Henry W. Mack/West Little River K-8 Center

data.description: Great investment property for those Investors looking for a under-market value deal. This is a legal triplex with a 2 bedroom 1 bath, 1 bed 1 bath and a standalone studio in the back. Enough parking for all units. Tenants are month to month and have been living in the property for many years. Property was renovated a few years back. Property has Impact windows, new floors, new kitchens, plumbing, electrical and much more! Market rents for all 3 units is around $4,500 a month. Also look at comps, all triplex in the area are closing for above $600k so this is a great deal!
